### Accommodation HTTP tests for AccommodationServiceImpl via AccommodationController

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@accommodationId = 3
@hostId = 7

### Create a new accommodation
POST {{baseUrl}}/accommodations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "host": {
    "id": {{hostId}}
  },
  "title": "Alojamiento céntrico y cómodo",
  "description": "Apartamento completamente amoblado cerca al centro",
  "city": "Armenia",
  "address": "Cra 10 #20-30",
  "latitude": 4.5333,
  "longitude": -75.6833,
  "priceDay": 120000,
  "guestsCount": 2,
  "averageRating": 0.0,
  "publicationDate": "2025-10-01",
  "status": "ACTIVE",
  "services": ["WIFI", "PARKING"],
  "images": [],
  "comments": []
}

### Get accommodation details by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/accommodations/{{accommodationId}}

### Search accommodations with filters
GET {{baseUrl}}/accommodations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "city": "Armenia",
  "fechaCheckIn": "2025-10-10",
  "fechaCheckOut": "2025-10-12",
  "minPrice": 0,
  "maxPrice": 300000,
  "guestsCount": 2,
  "services": ["WIFI"],
  "page": 0
}

### Verify availability of an accommodation
GET {{baseUrl}}/accommodations/{{accommodationId}}/availability?checkIn=2025-10-15&checkOut=2025-10-18

### List my accommodations (paged)
GET {{baseUrl}}/accommodations/my-accomodations?page=0

### List comments of an accommodation
GET {{baseUrl}}/accommodations/{{accommodationId}}/comments

### Update an accommodation (placeholder endpoint)
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/accommodations/{{accommodationId}}

### Delete an accommodation
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/accommodations/{{accommodationId}}

